  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p732356/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p align=\"left\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201505/0b2dad26e8c44fe1a992cf21c59efa04.jpg\" /></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\tPart 1 of the IELTS Speaking test is supposed to be easy. You don't need to give 'difficult' answers, and you should try to avoid making mistakes.雅思口语的第一部分应该来说比较简单。你不用给出复杂的答案，而且应该试图避免犯错。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Here are five simple rules for Speaking Part 1:</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">下面是关于口语第一部分的</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">5</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">条简单守则：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t1.Keep your answers short, then stop with confidence.回答要短，结束时要自信。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t2.Answer the questions using full sentences.用完整句回答。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t3.Use words from the examiner's question in your answer.在答案中用考官问题里的单词。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t4.If possible, give a reason for your answer.如果可以，给出答案的原因。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t5.Don't forget to say &quot;yes&quot; or &quot;no&quot; when necessary.需要时，别忘了说yes或no。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Here's an example to illustrate these points:</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">下面是演示上述守则的一个例子：</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\tDo you like parks?</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\tYes, I like parks because they are great places to relax. If you live in a city, a park is often the only place where you can escape from the noise and the traffic.</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p732356/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p732356\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p732177/\">悼念纳什：《美丽心灵》十大经典台词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p732176/\">美丽心灵原型诺贝尔奖得主纳什车祸去世</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731766/\">非高跟女星不让进 戛纳着装要求惹争议</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731315/\">男人心声：你的10个细节令他偷偷高兴（上）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731814/\">夜猫子还是早起的鸟儿？基因来定夺</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p732075/\">为治疗贫血 柬埔寨穷人煮“铁鱼”吃</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731658/\">坑！16个被翻译大神们误导的常识（上）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p732218/\">献给丢失爱情的你：戛纳获奖短片Sign笔记</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p732242/\">2015戛纳国际电影节获奖名单</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731655/\">An apple a day 这些老掉牙英文你还说吗？</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
